questions.explanation:
The data set homework will have missing values under the age variable. The name has a blank in it so we need to use the & list modifier to read the data, also when using this we have to make sure that the data are at least two spaces apart.
As SAS considers missing values smaller than 10 in age variable so it has included all the three observation in the data set.
The corrected code is as follows:
Data homewo;
input fname$ lname $ age height;
if age LE 10;
datalines;
John McCloskey 35 71
June Rosesette 10 43
Tineke Jones 9 37
;
run;

